item.title: 8. String to Integer (atoi)
item.description: LeetCode problem // .js /** * @param {string} s * @return {number} */ var myAtoi = function(s) { let res = 0; let num = parseInt(s); if(num >= 2147483648){ res = 2147483647; } else if (num <= -2147483648){ res = -2147483648; } else if (isNaN(num)) { res = 0; } else { res = num; } return res; };
